modelvariables.name: Veins.concentration_start[1]
modelvariables.description: * Amounts of all base molecules. If size is nS then mass fractions are scaled all base substance masses to sum=1 (this is not a good idea for non-gaseous solutions). If size is nS-2 then last but one substance is calculated from electroneutrality and last substance from specific volumes.

If size is nS-2 then last but one substance is calculated from electroneutrality and last substance from specific volumes.
